  "body": "### Describe the bug\n\nCalling `/eth/v1/beacon/states/head/committees` on the API endpoint always returns committees for slot 0, for example on the current deneb testnet:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl -s 'https://xxx@bn.lodestar-ethereumjs-1.srv.4844-devnet-6.ethpandaops.io/eth/v1/beacon/states/head/committees'| jq -r .data[].slot | sort | uniq -c\r\n     32 0\r\n```\n\n### Expected behavior\n\nWould expect to see the committees for the current epoch, for example:\r\n\r\n```\r\ncurl -s 'https://xxx@bn.teku-nethermind-1.srv.4844-devnet-6.ethpandaops.io/eth/v1/beacon/states/head/committees'| jq -r .data[].slot | sort | uniq -c\r\n      1 38176\r\n      1 38177\r\n      1 38178\r\n      1 38179\r\n      1 38180\r\n      1 38181\r\n      1 38182\r\n      1 38183\r\n      1 38184\r\n      1 38185\r\n      1 38186\r\n      1 38187\r\n      1 38188\r\n      1 38189\r\n      1 38190\r\n      1 38191\r\n      1 38192\r\n      1 38193\r\n      1 38194\r\n      1 38195\r\n      1 38196\r\n      1 38197\r\n      1 38198\r\n      1 38199\r\n      1 38200\r\n      1 38201\r\n      1 38202\r\n      1 38203\r\n      1 38204\r\n      1 38205\r\n      1 38206\r\n      1 38207\r\n```\n\n### Steps to reproduce\n\nAs per above, connected to pre-devnet 6\n\n### Additional context\n\n_No response_\n\n### Operating system\n\nLinux\n\n### Lodestar version or commit hash\n\nWhatever is running on the servers as mentioned above",
